export enum TSDayOfWeek {
    MONDAY = <any> 'MONDAY',
    TUESDAY = <any> 'TUESDAY',
    WEDNESDAY = <any> 'WEDNESDAY',
    THURSDAY = <any> 'THURSDAY',
    FRIDAY = <any> 'FRIDAY',
    SATURDAY = <any> 'SATURDAY',
    SUNDAY = <any> 'SUNDAY'
}

export function getWeekdaysValues(): Array<TSDayOfWeek> {
    return [
        TSDayOfWeek.MONDAY,
        TSDayOfWeek.TUESDAY,
        TSDayOfWeek.WEDNESDAY,
        TSDayOfWeek.THURSDAY,
        TSDayOfWeek.FRIDAY
    ];
}
